-- Russia Seeks At Least $3 Billion for 10% Stake in VTB, Shuvalov Says
-- B y   I l y a   A r k h i p o v
-- 2010-10-12T10:11:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/russia-seeks-at-least-3-billion-for-10-stake-in-vtb-shuvalov-says.html
Russia may sell a 10 percent stake
in VTB Group for at least $3 billion, said First Deputy Prime
Minister Igor Shuvalov.  Russia may sell the stake this year, Shuvalov told
reporters in Moscow today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
